#Normalizing all numeric predictors, basic log transformation

colClass <- sapply(FullHouse.imp, class)
logtransform <- function(x){
    x <- log(1+x)
  
  x
}

numericCols <- setdiff(names(colClass[colClass == "integer" | colClass == "num"]),c("Id","is.train"))
